Symbol.Script_3D:
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN 999
PEN gs_cont_pen MATERIAL gs_lbeam_mat if not(gs_shadow) then shadow off
Unid=1
! Length
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, 0, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
ROTx angy
! >>> Width (Bottom) HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID,B2,1+128, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-b2,0,unID,B2,2, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,1,0,unID,B2,3, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID,B2,1+128, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,b2,0,unID,B2,2, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-1,0,unID,B2,3, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,B2,1+128, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-b2,0,unID,B2,2, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,1,0,unID,B2,3, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,B2,1+128, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,b2,0,unID,B2,2, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-1,0,unID,B2,3, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1
! >>> Width (Top) HOTSPOT A,-B/2,ZZYZX,unID,lbeam_w2,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-B/2+lbeam_w2,ZZYZX,unID,lbeam_w2,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-B/2-1,ZZYZX,unID,lbeam_w2,3 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,-B/2,ZZYZX,unID,lbeam_w2,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-B/2+lbeam_w2,ZZYZX,unID,lbeam_w2,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-B/2-1,ZZYZX,unID,lbeam_w2,3 : unID=unID+1
! >>> Height HOTSPOT 0,-B/2,0,unID,ZZYZX,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-B/2,ZZYZX,unID,ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-B/2,-1,unID,ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,-B/2,0,unID,ZZYZX,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-B/2,ZZYZX,unID,ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-B/2,-1,unID,ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1
! >>> Height (Top) HOTSPOT 0,B/2,ZZYZX,unID,lbeam_h1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,B/2,ZZYZX-lbeam_h1,unID,lbeam_h1,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,B/2,ZZYZX+1,unID,lbeam_h1,3 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,B/2,ZZYZX,unID,lbeam_h1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B/2,ZZYZX-lbeam_h1,unID,lbeam_h1,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B/2,ZZYZX+1,unID,lbeam_h1,3 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,-B/2+lbeam_w2,ZZYZX,unID,lbeam_h1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-B/2+lbeam_w2,ZZYZX-lbeam_h1,unID,lbeam_h1,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-B/2+lbeam_w2,ZZYZX+1,unID,lbeam_h1,3 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,-B/2+lbeam_w2,ZZYZX,unID,lbeam_h1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-B/2+lbeam_w2,ZZYZX-lbeam_h1,unID,lbeam_h1,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-B/2+lbeam_w2,ZZYZX+1,unID,lbeam_h1,3 : unID=unID+1
FOR w=1 TO nn PUT GET (2), MAX (-1, 15*GET (1)) NEXT w
ROTz 90 ROTx 90 PRISM_ NSP/3, a, GET (NSP) DEL 2
DEL 1
999: FOR w=1 TO NSP qq= GET (1) NEXT w
END
Symbol.Script_2D:
Unid=1
! --- Length
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
! --- Length/2
HOTSPOT2 A/2,0,unID : unID=unID+1
Unid=10 ! --- Width if ABS(angy)<EPS AND only_axis=0 then !! angy=0
! --- Width (Bottom) HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,B2,1+128, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-b2,unID,B2,2, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,1,unID,B2,3, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,B2,1+128, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,b2,unID,B2,2, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-1,unID,B2,3, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,B2,1+128, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-b2,unID,B2,2, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,1,unID,B2,3, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,B2,1+128, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,b2,unID,B2,2, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-1,unID,B2,3, lbeam_w1 : unID=unID+1
! --- Width (Top) HOTSPOT2 A,-B/2,unID,lbeam_w2,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-B/2+lbeam_w2,unID,lbeam_w2,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-B/2-1,unID,lbeam_w2,3 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,-B/2,unID,lbeam_w2,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-B/2+lbeam_w2,unID,lbeam_w2,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-B/2-1,unID,lbeam_w2,3 : unID=unID+1
endif
PEN gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type Unid=100 hLineID = 1000
angy2=angy
if only_axis=0 then
cang= COS (angy2) sang= SIN (angy2) y1= -b/2*cang y2= b/2*cang y3= y1-zzyzx*sang y4= y3+w2*cang y6= y2-(zzyzx-h1)*sang y5= y6-(w1-w2)*cang ymin= MIN (y1, y2, y3, y4, y5, y6) ymax= MAX (y1, y2, y3, y4, y5, y6)
POLY2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, ymin, 1, 0, ymax, 1, a, ymax, 1, a, ymin, 1, 0, ymin, -1
if ABS(angy)>EPS then !! angy<>0 HOTSPOT2 0, ymin,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, ymin,unID : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0, ymax,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, ymax,unID : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0, y1,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 a, y1,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, y2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 a, y2,unID : unID=unID+1 endif
if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED then HOTLINE2 0, -b/2*COS(angy), a, -b/2*COS(angy), hLineID : hLineID = hLineID + 1 HOTLINE2 0, b/2*COS(angy), a, b/2*COS(angy), hLineID : hLineID = hLineID + 1 if y1<y3 then LINE_TYPE 1 else LINE_TYPE DetailLineType LINE2 0, y1, a, y1 if y6<y2 then LINE_TYPE 1 else LINE_TYPE DetailLineType LINE2 0, y2, a, y2 LINE_TYPE 1 if ABS (y3-y1)>0.0001 then LINE2 0, y3, a, y3 LINE2 0, y4, a, y4 if y4<y5 then LINE_TYPE 1 else LINE_TYPE DetailLineType LINE2 0, y5, a, y5 if y4<y6 THEN LINE_TYPE 1 else LINE_TYPE DetailLineType LINE2 0, y6, a, y6 LINE_TYPE 1 endif endif
if showsect AND only_axis=0 then LINE_TYPE 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, pos_2Dx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -1', unID, pos_2Dx, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 pos_2Dx, 0, unID, pos_2Dx, 2 : unID=unID+1 ADD2 pos_2Dx, 0 ROT2 90+angy2 FILL cross_fill POLY2_ NSP/3, 7, GET (NSP) DEL 2 endif
if axis then PEN axis_pen LINE_TYPE axis_line_type HOTLINE2 0, 0, a, 0, hLineID : hLineID = hLineID + 1 LINE2 0, 0, a, 0 endif
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! iObjectCode PRE_BEAM_LEDGER = 9
rrr = request("Working_length_unit", "", w_units_form) bMetricDimension = strstr(w_units_form, "m") ! m, cm, mm
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iDet2D DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE = 1 DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED = 2
EPS=0.0001
! *** Cross-section Data ***
PUT zzyzx, lbeam_w1, lbeam_w2, lbeam_h1
if NSP>0 then zz= GET (1) w1= GET (1) w2= GET (1) h1= GET (1) zzyzx= zz PARAMETERS zzyzx=zz PARAMETERS b=w1 b= MAX (w1, w2) nn= 6 PUT -w1/2+0.001, 0, 1, -w1/2+0.001, zz, 1, -w1/2+w2, zz, 1, -w1/2+w2, zz-h1, 1, w1/2, zz-h1, 1, w1/2, 0, 1 endif

Symbol.Script_VL:
hideparameter all "A", "B", "Zzyzx"
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` values{2} "iDet2D" DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE, `Простой`
VALUES "a" RANGE (0.3, ) LOCK "b" VALUES "angy" RANGE (-90, 90) VALUES "lbeam_w1" RANGE [lbeam_w2+0.05, ) VALUES "lbeam_w2" RANGE [0.05, lbeam_w1-0.05] VALUES "lbeam_h1" RANGE [0.05, zzyzx-0.1] VALUES "zzyzx" RANGE [0.2, ) VALUES "pos_2Dx" RANGE (zzyzx, a) VALUES "B2" RANGE [(lbeam_w2+0.05)/2, )
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME ="B2" then lbeam_w1 = B2*2 PARAMETERS lbeam_w1 = lbeam_w1 else B2 = lbeam_w1/2 PARAMETERS B2 = B2 endif
if LibraryLangCode = "USA" then VALUES "lbeam_sectype" "18LBxx", "20LBxx", "26LBxx", "Custom"
if lbeam_sectype="18LBxx" then VALUES "lbeam_type" "18LB18/8", "18LB24/12", "18LB32/20", "18LB36/20", "18LB36/24" endif
if lbeam_sectype="20LBxx" then VALUES "lbeam_type" "20LB20/12", "20LB24/12", "20LB28/16", "20LB32/20", "20LB36/24", "20LB40/24", "20LB44/28", "20LB48/32", "20LB52/36", "20LB56/40", "20LB60/44" endif
if lbeam_sectype="26LBxx" then VALUES "lbeam_type" "20LB26/12", "26LB24/12", "26LB28/16", "26LB32/20", "26LB36/24", "26LB40/24", "26LB44/28", "26LB48/32", "26LB52/36", "26LB56/40", "26LB60/44" endif
if lbeam_sectype="Custom" then lock "lbeam_type" endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "lbeam_type" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "lbeam_sectype" then if lbeam_sectype<>"Custom" then qq0= "" qq1= "" qq= SPLIT (lbeam_type, "%n%s%n%s%n", xx, qq0, yy, qq1, hh) zzyzx = yy*0.0254 lbeam_w1 = xx*0.0254 lbeam_w2 = xx*0.0254-8" lbeam_h1 = hh*0.0254 parameters zzyzx = zzyzx, lbeam_w1 = lbeam_w1, lbeam_w2 = lbeam_w2, lbeam_h1 = lbeam_h1 endif endif
! set back to custom if main parameters are changed if lbeam_sectype <> "Custom" then if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ZZYZX" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "lbeam_w1" or \ GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "lbeam_w2" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "lbeam_h1" then lbeam_sectype = "Custom" parameters lbeam_sectype = lbeam_sectype endif endif else hideparameter "lbeam_sectype", "lbeam_type" endif
if not(axis) then parameters only_axis=0 lock "only_axis", "axis_line_type", "axis_pen" endif if not(showsect) then lock "cross_fill" endif if axis and only_axis then lock "gs_fill_type", "gs_fill_pen", "gs_back_pen", "showsect", "cross_fill", "iDet2D", "DetailLineType", "gs_cont_pen" endif
if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE OR ABS(angy)<EPS then !! angy=0 lock "DetailLineType" endif
FOR w=1 TO NSP/3 PUT GET (2) qq= GET (1) NEXT w IF NSP>0 THEN PUT 1 PUT GET (NSP-1) ENDIF
IF gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=10 IF gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=19
es_length = a es_surface = (b*zzyzx-lbeam_h1*abs(lbeam_w2-lbeam_w1)) es_volume = es_surface*es_length PARAMETERS es_length=es_length, es_surface = es_surface, es_volume = es_volume
CALL "Precast_quantity_calc" parameters A = A, bMetricDimension = bMetricDimension, es_density = es_density, es_density_us = es_density_us, es_volume = es_volume, es_surface = es_surface
